                           <h3>Major Features of Bihar ECCE:</h3>
                           <div class=" ps-3">
                            <p><b>. Anganwadi Centers:</b> Anganwadi centers serve as the core facilities for delivering early childhood care and education across rural and urban areas of Bihar.</p>
                            <p> <b>. Curriculum:</b> A well-designed, child-centric curriculum that incorporates play-based learning, storytelling, and hands-on activities to foster creativity and curiosity.</p>
                            <p> <b>. Inclusion:</b> Ensures equitable access to quality education for children from marginalized communities and differently-abled children.</p>
                            <p> <b> . Monitoring & Evaluation: </b> Regular assessments to track the learning progress of children and enhance the effectiveness of the program.</p>
                            <p>By investing in Early Childhood Care & Education, Bihar aims to transform the early learning landscape, empowering its youngest citizens to lead healthier, happier, and more productive lives.</p>
                 
